  "detailed_description": "Cyberfusion is a roguelike, physics-based, full-body FPS that immerses you in a futuristic battlefield. Featuring cybernetic implants and procedurally generated levels, this game challenges you to adapt and survive in a world where your body is your ultimate weapon.<br><br><strong>Step into the future where cutting-edge technology meets human potential!</strong><br><br>At the pinnacle of cybernetic enhancement, Horizon Lab is pioneering the fusion of human and machine to create the ultimate innovations of tomorrow.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2934110/extras/a4f9c39ace695b53ba22b3ceab6432d1.poster.avif?t=1740680457\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2934110/extras/a4f9c39ace695b53ba22b3ceab6432d1.webm?t=1740680457\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2934110/extras/a4f9c39ace695b53ba22b3ceab6432d1.mp4?t=1740680457\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES:</h2><br>- <strong>Enhance Your Skills: </strong>Equip a range of cyber implants to boost your abilities beyond human limits.<br>- <strong>Dynamic Combat: </strong>Experience realistic, physics-based interactions between players, enemies, and weapons for thrilling battles.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2934110/extras/28491864dcdbac4dd7f04aaeaa472081.poster.avif?t=1740680457\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2934110/extras/28491864dcdbac4dd7f04aaeaa472081.webm?t=1740680457\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2934110/extras/28491864dcdbac4dd7f04aaeaa472081.mp4?t=1740680457\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>- <strong>Full-Body Immersion:</strong> Play as a fully-rendered character, bringing a new level of immersion.<br>- <strong>Diverse Levels: </strong>Embark on a journey through a multitude of randomly generated game levels, each presenting unique challenges and surprises for players to navigate through.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2934110/extras/eaf6e7324068179c6f26779876b1873b.poster.avif?t=1740680457\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2934110/extras/eaf6e7324068179c6f26779876b1873b.webm?t=1740680457\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2934110/extras/eaf6e7324068179c6f26779876b1873b.mp4?t=1740680457\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>- <strong>Weapon Evolution: </strong>Upgrade any weapon to unleash its full potential and customize your arsenal to suit your playstyle.<br><br><strong>Horizon Lab invites you </strong>to experience the future of technology, where your body becomes the ultimate tool.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2934110/extras/fb1806c44e758b184b1f50061d9ac576.poster.avif?t=1740680457\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2934110/extras/fb1806c44e758b184b1f50061d9ac576.webm?t=1740680457\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2934110/extras/fb1806c44e758b184b1f50061d9ac576.mp4?t=1740680457\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Join the revolution! Embrace the future!</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2934110/extras/aa05907e0ddd252006e9abea69a00b1d.poster.avif?t=1740680457\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2934110/extras/aa05907e0ddd252006e9abea69a00b1d.webm?t=1740680457\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2934110/extras/aa05907e0ddd252006e9abea69a00b1d.mp4?t=1740680457\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
